{
  "texts": [
    "These strategies can be influenced by factors such as proficiency level, confidence, and exposure to the target language.",
    "LLMs-surprisals do not provide insight into the cognitive or strategic processes behind language production decisions.",
    "They simply reflect how unexpected a construction is based on large-scale native language usage.",
    "Last but not the least, we need to consider the corpus-based nature of LLMs-surprisals.",
    "LLMs are trained on extensive corpora of mostly native speaker data, and LLMs-surprisal values reflect patterns in this data."
  ]
}